{"thi-ap13:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap13:0.2":"Ekuposathikavagga ","thi-ap13:0.3":"Modakadayikatheriapadana ","thi-ap13:1.1":"“Nagare bandhumatiya, ","thi-ap13:1.2":"kumbhadasi ahosaham; ","thi-ap13:1.3":"Mama bhagam gahetvana, ","thi-ap13:1.4":"gaccham udakaharika. ","thi-ap13:2.1":"Panthamhi samanam disva, ","thi-ap13:2.2":"santacittam samahitam; ","thi-ap13:2.3":"Pasannacitta sumana, ","thi-ap13:2.4":"modake tinidasaham. ","thi-ap13:3.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap13:3.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap13:3.3":"Ekanavutikappani, ","thi-ap13:3.4":"vinipatam nagacchaham. ","thi-ap13:4.1":"Sampatti tam karitvana, ","thi-ap13:4.2":"sabbam anubhavim aham; ","thi-ap13:4.3":"Modake tini datvana, ","thi-ap13:4.4":"pattaham acalam padam. ","thi-ap13:5.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap13:5.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap13:5.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap13:6.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap13:6.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap13:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap13:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap13:7.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap13:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap13:8.1":"Ittham sudam modakadayika bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap13:9.1":"Modakadayikatheriyapadanam tatiyam. "}